This paper deals with the capacity region of the simultaneous relay channel and the broadcast relay channel, which are both related to information theory. Therefore, cs.IT (Information Theory) is the most likely sub-category. The paper also discusses cooperative strategies and coding schemes, which are related to networking and communication, making cs.NI (Networking and Internet Architecture) a likely sub-category as well. The paper also mentions the use of Gaussian models, which falls under cs.MM (Multimedia) and cs.CE (Computational Engineering, Finance, and Science) may also be relevant due to the mathematical nature of the paper.
